game.name: Freddy Pharkas - Frontier Pharmacist (1993) (Sierra On-Line) (Floppy Version).dosz
game.comment: Installed from 3.5" floppy disks matching with TGOD ID: 223 Installation options: Graphics: VGA or IBM PS2 - 256 Colors (Default) Music: Sound Blaster Pro Audio: Sound Blaster (Default) Joystick: Don't use a joystick (Default) Mouse: Use Microsoft compatible mouse (Default) Memory: Use your machine's extra memory (Default) Directory: C:\SIERRA\FPFP (Default) Say Yes to using samples Then in RESOURCE.CFG, delete line 8 ( directory = \SIERRA\FPFP) RESOURCE.CFG is needed in the DOSZ to run the game. Almost matches with GOG, except for RESOURCE.CFG RESOURCE.CFG is provided in the DOSC, or it can be generated by DoDAT using the embedded data
game.comment_dosc: Required RESOURCE.CFG and auto start. MT-32 option. CPU speed reduced to make Sound Blaster Pro driver work
